</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_55" id="26r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Dem <expan>erb<ex>er</ex>n</expan> und weisen Nyclasen Vintler, auf dem
                        Runkenstein <expan>gesesse<ex>n</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>besund<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gute<ex>n</ex></expan> günner </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> her Vintler, als
                                    <add><expan>Eberh<ex>art</ex></expan></add> Kügellein,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, yeczund czu <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<add><expan>gned<ex>igen</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>herczog<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>Fr<ex>idrich</ex></expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Oster<ex>reich</ex></expan></add>, kumt <add>umb</add>
<expan>ein<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>bestetigu<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
<add>von <expan>de<ex>m</ex>selb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, <expan>hercz<ex>og</ex></expan>
<expan>Frid<ex>rich</ex></expan></add>, der brief und freyheit, als
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> und kauffleute mit
                            <expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan> hab und kauffmanschaft von den
                                <expan>durchl<ex>euhtigen</ex></expan>,
                            <expan>hochg<ex>eporen</ex></expan>
<expan>fürste<ex>n</ex></expan> und <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, herczog
                                <expan>Rudolffe<ex>n</ex></expan> und herczog
                                <expan>Albr<ex>echt</ex></expan>, <expan>seine<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        vettern, und herczog <expan>Leupold<ex>en</ex></expan>, seine<ex>m</ex>
                        vater <expan>selig<ex>en</ex></expan> gedehtnüsse, und auch herczog
                                <expan>Leupold<ex>en</ex></expan>, <expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan>
                        pruder, von <expan>Oster<ex>reich</ex></expan> etc.,
                                <expan>uns<ex>e</ex>re<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, durch ire lande, herschaft und gepiete
                        sicher zu varen, zu wandeln und zu arbeyten begnadet und gefreyet sein.
                            <add>Also</add>
<expan>bite<ex>n</ex></expan>
<add>wir</add>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> erberkeit mit <expan>alle<ex>m</ex></expan>
                        fleisz, daz ir durch <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> dem <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<add>freuntlich</add>
<expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
<add>und</add>
<expan>gute<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> gen <expan>demselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, herczog <expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan>,
                            <add>günstiklich</add> beweisen wöllet, daz uns die <add>selb
                                    <expan>bestetigu<ex>n</ex>g</expan></add> von
                                <expan>seine<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> werde, als wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>freuntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> des besunder wol
                                <expan>getr<ex>awen</ex></expan>. Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        wir umb <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>allcz<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>dienen</expan>.</ab>
</div>
